<L>__{exterior cross roads day}
<A>__{jack stops the car. at the crossroads is a signpost pointing to the town. the sign reads:}
<B>__{castelvecchio.}
<L>__{interior car continuous}
<A>__{jack looks at the sign. he looks up at the silent town, at the vast stone ramparts. an old man comes out of a crooked medieval doorway, stares at jack and disappears into another building. jack looks at the dead sockets of the windows, random beneath the rotting patchwork of rooves. a dog barks. the wind hisses. the atmosphere is deathly. jack makes a decision. and drives away.}
